---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="About – TrendSeek" description="About TrendSeek: your source for in-depth analysis on trending topics in technology, finance, science, and economy." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="container about-page">
      <h1>About TrendSeek</h1>

      <p><strong>TrendSeek</strong> is your intelligent guide to the topics shaping our world. We deliver in-depth, well-researched articles on the most important trends in <strong>technology, finance, science, economy, and history</strong> — available in English, Italian, Spanish, and French.</p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>In a world overflowing with information, finding thoughtful and reliable analysis can be challenging. TrendSeek exists to cut through the noise. We combine deep research with editorial quality to bring you articles that are:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Well-researched</strong> — backed by data, studies, and expert insights</li>
        <li><strong>Accessible</strong> — complex topics explained clearly for everyone</li>
        <li><strong>Multilingual</strong> — available in 4 languages to reach a global audience</li>
        <li><strong>SEO-optimized</strong> — easy to find when you need them most</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>What We Cover</h2>
      <p>Our articles span a wide range of trending and niche topics:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>🔬 <strong>Science &amp; Technology</strong> — Quantum computing, AI, cybersecurity, emerging tech</li>
        <li>💰 <strong>Finance &amp; Investing</strong> — Options strategies, market analysis, personal finance</li>
        <li>🌍 <strong>Economy &amp; Geopolitics</strong> — Global trends, trade policies, economic shifts</li>
        <li>🚀 <strong>Startups &amp; Entrepreneurship</strong> — Bootstrapping, growth strategies, innovation</li>
        <li>📜 <strong>History &amp; Culture</strong> — Fascinating historical events, civilizations, and untold stories</li>
      </ul>



      <h2>Stay Informed</h2>
      <p>Bookmark <a href="/">trendseek.net</a> and check back regularly for fresh content. New articles are published daily, covering the latest developments across our core topics.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
        Have questions or suggestions? Reach out at <strong>trendseek.net@gmail.com</strong>
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .about-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .about-page ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .about-page li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .about-page a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
